1411299[=]ustv[=]yanmjie[=]悍然剧透——DH的[=]2007-01-26 19:03:43[=]一个DH 整个SEASON 3的剧透+翻译……（不一定真实） 虽然说不能保证真实，但是看着觉得还有点道理……大家看着玩吧。 1. Orsen Hodge is a contract killer who worked for Noah Taylor (Zach's rich grandfather). Before he died he sent Orsen to murder Mike out of revenge, and becoming unloyal to him before he died. Monique (most recent dead girl found) was also a contract hit who had affairs with several successfully rich men, including Laurie Metclaf's husband, and Noah Taylor. She tried to black mail Noah but he sent Orsen to kill her. Orsen是个金钱杀手，曾经为Noah Taylor（Zach的爷爷）工作。在他死之前为了报复他雇佣了Orsen去杀Mike，因为Mike对Noah的不忠。Monique（就是S3E6 闪回里出现的女人，也就是最近发现的死尸）其实Monique也是个金钱杀手的目标，Monique跟很多有钱男人发生过关系，包括Laurie的老公和 Noah Taylor。Monique之前想要以某种原由威胁Noah最后被Noah雇佣的Orsen杀掉。 2. Mike who worked for Noah, was going to kill Monique for Noah as his first hit as a contract killer, but backed out when after starting a fake relationship with her he fell in love with her and decided he would not kill for Noah. Instead Noah hired Orsen to kill her. Mike之前也是为Noah工作的，本来Noah是雇佣Mike去杀Monique，但是Mike后来在企图接近Monique的时候爱上了Monique所以决定不去杀她。后来Noah就雇佣了Orsen去杀Monique了。 3. Orsen Hodge did not kill his wife. But helped induce her into a fragil mental state, and locked her up in the psychiatric hospital, where he went to visit her when he met Bree. Orsen没有杀他的妻子。但是是他导致了Alma的神经问题，然后把Alma放在了精神病医院。也就是那个时候他遇到Bree。（插花：这点有待商榷，因为之前Orsen在医院看望的人跟Alma的演员不是一个人，但是不排除整容的可能。） 4. Orsen Hodge's meeting of Bree was not coincidental, he is out to murder her, and the person who called the hit is someone who you won't suspect. (NOTE the writers have not indicated who the person will be) Orsen遇到Bree并不是巧合，Orsen的目的是杀Bree，具体是被谁雇佣，这点会是一个惊悚点。（具体是谁没有说。） 5. Lynette's marriage will fall by the end of the season. Lynette的婚姻在SEASON 3结束时会破裂。 6. Gabbie and Carlos will reunite and finally have a baby by the end of the season. Gabbie和Carlos会复合，在S3结尾他们会有一个他们自己的小孩。 7. Mike's memory will return, but Susan has moved on with a new man and will not go back to him at all for the rest of the season. Mike的记忆会恢复，但是Susan已经跟了另一个人，而且在整个SEASON 3都不会再跟Mike复合。 8. Three minor characters will die this year, 1)Orsen 2)Nora 3)one of Bree's children 三个小角色会死。 1. Orsen 2. Nora 3. Bree孩子中的一个 9. Bree runs for city councellor only to have her shady family history made public by her opponent. Bree竞选City Councellor，但是她的对手把Bree的黑历史都挖了出来。 10. Edie's nephew and Julie start dating, but he breaks it off when she insists on saving her virginity until she's married (much to susan's delight) Edie的侄子和Julie会开始交往，但是因为Julie坚持反对婚前性行为（这句我翻译的时候我自己都想笑~）而分手。 http://www.friends6.com/forum/thread-53733-1-1.html  
